      "content": "that makes sense, thanks. but i'm looking at the actual diagram in my textbook and the way the branches are laid out looks so messy. like, when the tree gets really deep with all those sub-branches for the prepositional phrase, it's hard to keep track of which node connects to what. is there a better way to visualize these complex trees so the structure is clearer?",
