      "role": "user",
      "content": "i tried the dependency diagrams but it's still a bit overwhelming. especially when the branches start spreading out all over the place for long sentences. it almost feels like the more complex the sentence, the more chaotic the \"tree\" becomes. do you have any other tips for managing those huge, spreading branches so i don't lose my place?",
